car.shared.views3d.obj
Class Face

java.lang.Object
  car.shared.views3d.obj.Face

public class Face
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a face of a ObjWireFrame. The vertex and normal values index into the vertex and normal arrays of the enclosing ObjWireFrame .

Author:
Joshua Little
